dmca.title: Text and Image DMCA (Copyright) Complaint to Google

works.description:
The latest entrant into the family of  
incredible bling-bling vehicles that can bring the traffic to a halt is
the  
Swarovski-studded Audi from the tuning studio Shampar. Exhibited at the  
Moscow Tuning Show, which took place in the international exhibition
center  
Crocus Expo, this blinged Audi has its surface covered with 450,000  
Swarovski crystals.
